article.description: — D.J. Burns Jr. had 23 points as Winthrop defeated Hampton 69-57 on Saturday.
article.headline: Burns Jr. scores 23 to carry Winthrop over Hampton 69-57
article.linkText: Burns Jr. scores 23 to carry Winthrop over Hampton 69-57
article.story: HAMPTON, Va. -- — D.J. Burns Jr. had 23 points as Winthrop defeated Hampton 69-57 on Saturday. Kelton Talford had 12 points and 10 rebounds for Winthrop (15-8, 8-2 Big South Conference). Sin'Cere McMahon added 10 points. Drew Buggs had six rebounds. Russell Dean had 12 points for the Pirates (6-14, 2-7). Raymond Bethea Jr. added 10 points and seven rebounds. DeAngelo Epps had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
